# Active Connections and Integrations

## Zapier
Connects Claude to various third-party apps and services. Your active Zapier integrations include:

### Gmail
- Add labels, archive emails, create drafts and draft replies
- Delete emails, find emails, remove labels
- Reply to emails, send emails
- Full email management capabilities

### Google Calendar
- Add attendees to events, create detailed events, quick add events
- Delete events, find events, find busy periods
- Update events, retrieve events by ID
- Search by date, time, attendees, and more
- Full calendar management

### Google Docs
- Append text to existing documents
- Create documents from templates with variable replacement
- Create documents from text (supports limited HTML)
- Find documents by name
- Upload documents from other services

### Google Drive
- Add file sharing preferences, copy files, create files from text
- Create folders and shortcuts, delete files
- Find files and folders, move files
- Replace files, update file/folder names
- Upload files, retrieve files by ID
- Comprehensive file management

### Google Sheets
- Clear rows, copy worksheets, create multiple rows
- Create spreadsheets, create columns and rows
- Delete rows, find worksheets, format rows
- Get many rows (up to 1,500), lookup rows
- Update single or multiple rows
- Full spreadsheet manipulation

### Jira Software Cloud
- Add attachments, comments, and watchers to issues
- Create issues, find components and issues
- Find issues via JQL (Jira Query Language)
- Find projects and users, link issues
- Move issues to sprints, update issues
- Complete project management capabilities

### OneDrive
- Copy files/folders, create folders and text files
- Create sharing invitations and links
- Find drives, files, and folders by ID
- Search files and folders, upload files
- Microsoft cloud storage management

### Perplexity
- Chat completion with AI model
- Advanced field options for customized responses

### Reflect
- Append to daily notes
- Create links and notes
- Note-taking and knowledge management

### Todoist
- Add comments to projects and tasks
- Create projects and tasks
- Find projects, tasks, and users
- Get project collaborators, invite users
- Mark tasks complete, move tasks to sections
- Update tasks
- Complete task management

### Trello
- Add attachments, checklists, labels, and members
- Archive cards, close boards, complete checklist items
- Copy and create boards, create cards and lists
- Create checklist items and comments, create labels
- Delete checklists, find boards, cards, and members
- Move cards, remove labels, update cards
- Full Trello board management

### WhatsApp Notifications
- Send messages to WhatsApp users

## Figma (Direct Integration)
- Get design context and code from Figma files
- Get Code Connect mappings for components
- Get FigJam boards, metadata, screenshots
- Get variable definitions
- Create design system rules
- Full design-to-code workflow support

## Google Services (Direct Integration)

### Google Drive Search
- Semantic search across all your Drive files
- Search by content, metadata, dates, owners
- Find internal documents, policies, project files
- Best for proprietary/confidential information

### Google Drive Fetch
- Direct document content retrieval by ID
- Read Google Docs content directly
- More efficient than search for known documents

### Gmail (Direct Integration)
- Read your Gmail profile
- Search messages with advanced operators
- Read specific messages and full threads
- Access to complete email context

## System Tools
- **User Location**: Get your current location
- **User Time**: Get current time and timezone
- **Calendar Events**: Create, search, update, delete events
- **Reminders**: Create, search, update, delete reminders
- **Message Compose**: Draft emails and messages
- **Map Display**: Show locations on maps
- **Past Conversations**: Search through conversation history
- **Web Search & Fetch**: Search the web and retrieve content